reviewText: Absolutely Love the Series and Excellent reproduction of the original Tapes.
The title show is great, but the other shows.... Meh. There're actually kind of boring. I don't know that I'd recommend this one unless you're really bored.
I like this movie I remember the red shoe diaries when I was in my teen or young it still great movie
I enjoy all the red shoe diaries episodes from the TV series and would recommend them to anyone in the appropriate age group.

This is one of those series that was ahead of its time when it first came out. I first saw the movie that inspired the series because David Duchovney was in it and I was a fan of his. That led me to the series that was alot like mini movies for TV. This particulate was a group of three that was near the end of the series. Not as good as the ones at the start of the series, but defiently add to finish your collection.
